FBIS4-40284 "drsov116_a_94029" FBIS-SOV-94-116 Daily Report 15 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS World Bank To Grant 1 Billion Dollar Credit World Bank To Grant 1 Billion Dollar Credit LD1506140194 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1300 GMT 15 Jun 94 LD1506140194 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] The World Bank plans to give Russia a new credit of 1 billion dollars. The accord on the credit is to be signed next week during the forthcoming visit to the United States by Russian Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin. Half of the funds provided will be allocated to the fuel and energy complex and the other half to private farms.
